    "asOf": "2023-02-09",
    "date": "2023-05-22T18:52:49Z",
    "text": "Protecting Gun Owners in Bankruptcy Act of 2023\n\nThis bill modifies federal bankruptcy law to allow an individual debtor to exempt from their bankruptcy estate one or more firearms up to a total maximum value of $3,000. The bill also specifies that such firearms are household goods that are not subject to liens in bankruptcy."
